Description: Minimal Chromium-based browser focused on low RAM usage
 IlunyaBrowser is a lightweight web browser built on Qt WebEngine (Chromium).
 It provides Google search, multi-tab browsing, and aggressive memory
 optimizations for inactive tabs.
